            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Solo bloggers who want optimization basics without premium pricing.</div>
            <a href="https://neuronwriter.com" class="tool-cta-btn" rel="nofollow">Visit site →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
